    "summary": "I develop and apply advanced simulation methods to dissect and control complex biomolecular and soft matter systems, such as peptides, proteins, DNA, polysaccharides or colloids. The computational techniques that I work on reveal key energetics and mechanisms at the atomic or nano scale, and are extensible to diverse processes; including non-biological. I enjoy teamwork at the physics-chemistry-biology interface, as well as with experimentalists. My final goal is to design tunable and responsive, \"living-like\", materials to address today's challenges in sustainability and health.",
